      • TextField

        public TextField(Table table,

        Defines the field and initialCapacity (if not defined)
        Parameters:
        table - the table
        name - the name
        initialCapacity - Initial count of words for which space is reserved. Default value set by Catalog is 100 words.
        textIndex - the textIndex to use
